                Recruitment <span class="text-uae-red">Scams</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Protect yourself from fraudulent recruitment practices targeting Tanzanian job seekers
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <!-- Common Scam Types -->
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">Common Recruitment Scams</h3>

                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-50 to-pink-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-uae-red">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg text-uae-red mb-2">Fake Job Offers</h4>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
                            <li>• Promises of high salaries with no experience required</li>
                            <li>• Jobs that seem too good to be true</li>
                            <li>• Requests for payment to "secure" the position</li>
                            <li>• Unsolicited job offers via email or social media</li>
                            <li>• Companies not registered with UAE authorities</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-50 to-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-orange-600">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg text-orange-600 mb-2">Visa Fraud</h4>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
                            <li>• Agents charging exorbitant visa fees</li>
                            <li>• Fake visa processing services</li>
                            <li>• Promises of guaranteed visa approval</li>
                            <li>• Pressure to pay before visa is issued</li>
                            <li>• Agents not licensed by UAE immigration</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-50 to-indigo-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-purple-600">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg text-purple-600 mb-2">Document Forgery</h4>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
                            <li>• Fake employment contracts</li>
                            <li>• Forged work permits or licenses</li>
                            <li>• Altered educational certificates</li>
                            <li>• Counterfeit medical certificates</li>
                            <li>• Fake reference letters</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Protection Strategies -->
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">How to Protect Yourself</h3>

                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-50 to-emerald-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-tanzanian-green">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg text-tanzanian-green mb-2">Verification Steps</h4>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
                            <li>• Verify company registration with DED</li>
                            <li>• Check agent licenses with MOHRE</li>
                            <li>• Research company reviews and ratings</li>
                            <li>• Contact company directly using official channels</li>
                            <li>• Never pay for job placement services</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 p-6 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-tanzanian-blue">
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lg text-tanzanian-blue mb-2">Red Flags to Watch</h4>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
                            <li>• Requests for upfront payments</li>
                            <li>• Pressure to act quickly</li>
                            <li>• Poor English or unprofessional communication</li>
                            <li>• Lack of official company documentation</li>
                            <li>• Promises that seem unrealistic</li>
